summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property necessary for laying off, opening, widening and establishing Fifth Avenue North between Valley Street and Republican Street under Ordinance 100337, as supplemented by Ordinance 101501, King County Cause No. 746324; accepting the condemnation award for Parcel Two in connection therewith; and making an appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
